229
00:12:34,110 --> 00:12:35,910
I've already gotten word to you.

230
00:12:36,010 --> 00:12:36,960
I'm leaving.

231
00:12:48,060 --> 00:12:48,830
Tianhe.

232
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:52,260
