you think I was the son of a traitor.

242
00:13:11,430 --> 00:13:12,760
What you are thinking is

243
00:13:12,920 --> 00:13:13,490
that you want me

244
00:13:13,490 --> 00:13:15,490
to be kicked out by Qionghua, right?

245
00:13:21,390 --> 00:13:22,230
